ov V</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2015-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/254BB36C-6A6B-46DE-A889-63228C17C3FC"><gtr:id>254BB36C-6A6B-46DE-A889-63228C17C3FC</gtr:id><gtr:title>September Arctic sea-ice minimum predicted by spring melt-pond fraction</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Nature Climate Change</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/c36baab72a54dff27e081f3c0e0649bd"><gtr:id>c36baab72a54dff27e081f3c0e0649bd</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Schr?der D</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2014-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/B7CCCF02-1E43-4502-9C03-A7DE723374FD"><gtr:id>B7CCCF02-1E43-4502-9C03-A7DE723374FD</gtr:id><gtr:title>The effects of tides on the water mass mixing and sea ice in the Arctic Ocean</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Journal of Geophysical Research: Oceans</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/85c49bb44c3afcd144d82b88fbfba6eb"><gtr:id>85c49bb44c3afcd144d82b88fbfba6eb</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Luneva M</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2015-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/BBB931B8-749B-48EE-A041-21E10D20C92E"><gtr:id>BBB931B8-749B-48EE-A041-21E10D20C92E</gtr:id><gtr:title>Western Arctic Ocean freshwater storage increased by wind-driven spin-up of the Beaufort&amp;nbsp;Gyre</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Nature Geoscience</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/68e2bb0643f5faac307cd1c143447afe"><gtr:id>68e2bb0643f5faac307cd1c143447afe</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Giles K</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2012-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/15DBE7D8-3C99-4EC2-8932-FF2ABE977880"><g